title: Match History won't load.
body:
For about a month now every time I try to load up the online Match History, it stays blank and won't load up anything. 

At first I thought it was a site problem and it'd be fixed by itself eventually, but as of right now I'm the only one among my friend's who's having the issue.

Anyone have an idea what's causing it?

replies.body: This is caused by a bug with the page that we're aware of and are looking into a solution. I don't have an ETA on the fix to provide you with, but if you have any other questions, let me know!
Gotcha, at least I now know it's not on my end, thanks a lot ^^
